data.description: An adorable two bedroom home on a quiet cul-de-sac in the heart of Poughkeepsie. This well maintained home features a spacious kitchen, roomy bathroom, central air, original wood trim and molding with hardwood floors throughout. Washer and dryer included on the first floor, with plenty of storage and usable space in the full basement.  Brand new hot water heater and furnace, with gas fuel and town water/sewer.  A detached one car garage and backyard patio complete this move-in ready home. Conveniently located to schools, restaurants, Vassar College, Metro North and all Poughkeepsie's amenities.
